				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\sigma $$\end{document}) is constant with streamwise position (Tennekes and Lumley 1972; Pope 2000). Far-wake self-similarity facilitates the development of simple analytical models for the prediction of the mean flow distribution in this region, see Sect. 2.2.3.

